64
00:10:33,162 --> 00:10:48,220
Be this conceit of mine as it may, gentlemen, at all events steel-kilt was a tall and noble animal, with a head like a Roman, and a flowing golden beard like the tasseled housings of your last Viceroy's snorting charger.

