his face fiery red, his eyes bloodshot, and wiping the profuse sweat from his brow.

90
00:13:04,535 --> 00:13:12,064
Now what cozening fiend it was, gentlemen, that possessed Radney to meddle with such a man in that corporeally exasperated state!

91
00:13:13,005 --> 00:13:16,128
